graph TB
    subgraph "KServe Component"
        Controller[kserve-controller-manager<br/>Kubernetes Operator]
        Webhook[kserve-webhook-server<br/>Admission Webhook]
        Controller -->|validates/mutates via| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "Model Serving Infrastructure"
        StorageInit[storage-initializer<br/>Init Container]
        Agent[agent<br/>Sidecar Container]
        Router[router<br/>InferenceGraph Container]
        InferenceServer[Python Inference Servers<br/>sklearn/xgboost/tensorflow/pytorch/huggingface]

        StorageInit -->|downloads models| InferenceServer
        Agent -->|batching/logging| InferenceServer
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        InferenceServiceCR[InferenceService CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1beta1]
        ServingRuntimeCR[ServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        TrainedModelCR[TrainedModel CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        InferenceGraphCR[InferenceGraph CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
    end

    User[User/CI] -->|creates| InferenceServiceCR
    InferenceServiceCR -->|watched by| Controller
    ServingRuntimeCR -->|defines runtime| InferenceServer

    Controller -->|creates| KnativeService[Knative Service]
    Controller -->|creates| Deployment[Kubernetes Deployment]
    Controller -->|creates| VirtualService[Istio VirtualService]
    Controller -->|injects| StorageInit

    InferenceGraphCR -->|orchestrates| Router
    Router -->|routes to| InferenceServer

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        Istio[Istio 1.16+<br/>Service Mesh]
        Knative[Knative Serving 1.8+<br/>Serverless Platform]
        CertManager[cert-manager 1.10+<br/>Certificate Management]
    end

    Controller -->|depends on| Istio
    Controller -->|depends on| Knative
    Webhook -->|TLS certs from| CertManager

    subgraph "Internal ODH Dependencies"
        ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>gRPC API]
        S3Storage[S3 Storage<br/>Model Artifacts]
    end

    Controller -.->|fetches metadata| ModelRegistry
    StorageInit -->|downloads from| S3Storage

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style InferenceServiceCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style InferenceServer fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Istio fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Knative fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style ModelRegistry fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style S3Storage fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
